  ('VW_EA211_GTE_PHEV', 'VW EA211 1.4 TSI + DQ400e (GTE/e-tron PHEV)', 'Volkswagen', 1.4, 4, 'phev', 'belt', 210000, NULL, '5W-30 VW 504 00', 3.6, 'VW G13 (engine) + separate G13 inverter loop', 'premium', 15000, 12, 'Golf GTE MK7 RAH190-class, Audi A3 e-tron 8V, Passat GTE B8. Engine is EA211 — same cambelt anchor applies. DQ400e is the differentiating drivetrain (wet-clutch 6-speed DCT with integrated electric motor). HV battery 8.7kWh.'),
